column2: SELECT s.SpecObjID, s.z, s.fiberMag_r, s.mag_#, s.sn_#, L.ew, L.sigma, L.sigmaErr, K.ew, K.sigma, K.sigmaErr into mydb.MyTable from SpecObj as s, SpecLine as L, SpecLine as K WHERE (L.LineID = #) and (K.LineID = #) and s.SpecObjID = L.specObjID and L.specObjID = K.specObjID and L.ew/#if (L.ewErr, #) > # and s.z IS NOT # and s.sn_# > # and s.objType = # and s.z> # and s.z< # ORDER BY s.mag_#
